OL,3,C#1bn fund sees Shotton Mill become
OL,4,CUK's largest recycled paper
OL,5,Cmanufacturer
OL,7,FA Deeside site is set to become the
OL,8,FUK's largest recycled paper
OL,9,Fmanufacturer.
OL,11,FShotton Mill is the recipient of a
OL,12,F#1billion investment, which aims to
OL,13,Fsafeguard 147 existing jobs and create
OL,14,Fa further 220.
OL,16,FThe site was acquired by Eren Holding,
OL,17,Fa leading manufacturer from Turkey, in
OL,18,F2021.
