OL,7,FDeeside is one of the largest
OL,8,Findustrial parks in Europe, and this
OL,9,Finvestment aims to see the plant
OL,10,Frecycle wastepaper that would
OL,11,Fotherwise go overseas or into landfill.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government has also
OL,14,Fsupported the expansion, contributing
OL,15,F#13million in funding alongside
OL,16,F#136million in support from UK Export
OL,17,FFinance (UKEF), the UK government's
OL,18,Fexport credit agency.
