OL,5,Cmanufacturer
OL,7,FThey say the investment will boost the
OL,8,Flocal economy, as well as aiding the
OL,9,FUK's transition to net zero and
OL,10,Fcreating jobs in the green industries.
OL,12,FCabinet ministers from both the UK and
OL,13,FWelsh governments will visit the site
OL,14,Fto meet with members of the Eren
OL,15,FHolding group, where they will hear
OL,16,Fmore about the site's transformation.
