OL,3,C#1bn fund sees Shotton Mill become
OL,4,CUK's largest recycled paper
OL,5,Cmanufacturer
OL,7,FWales secretary Jo Stevens MP said:
OL,8,F"Deeside has a long and proud history
OL,9,Fas one of Wales' key industrial
OL,10,Fcentres and this significant
OL,11,Finvestment from our two governments
OL,12,Fwill secure jobs and help bring a
OL,13,Fprosperous future for the area."
OL,15,FWelsh Government economy secretary
OL,16,FRebecca Evans said the redevelopment
OL,17,Fshows how "commitment to a prosperous,
OL,18,Fgreen economy" leads to "investment"
OL,19,Fand "sustainable jobs", as well as
OL,20,Fwaste reduction.
