OL,7,FShe added: "Once fully operational,
OL,8,Finstead of transporting paper waste
OL,9,Fmany hundreds or thousands of miles
OL,10,Foverseas to be processed it will be
OL,11,Fturned into recycled packaging here in
OL,12,FWales.
OL,14,F"This, alongside the nature of the
OL,15,Ftechnology, means a net reduction in
OL,16,Fcarbon emissions equivalent to
OL,17,Femissions from 190,000 homes a year."
