OL,4,CUK's largest recycled paper
OL,5,Cmanufacturer
OL,7,FPlans for the plant will see it
OL,8,Fproduce nearly 100% recycled paper,
OL,9,Falongside an environmentally-friendly
OL,10,Fproduction model where it will purify
OL,11,Fits own wastewater, recycle and reuse
OL,12,Fit within the system.
OL,14,FUKEF supported the venture by issuing
OL,15,Fa guarantee which allows HSBC and
OL,16,FCredit Suisse to arrange debt
OL,17,Ffinancing for the project.
