OL,5,Cmanufacturer
OL,7,FThe Eren investment hopes to boost
OL,8,FWelsh and UK exports in paper, with
OL,9,FUKEF support offered on the
OL,10,Funderstanding that Shotton Mill will
OL,11,Fexport 10% of its turnover within five
OL,12,Fyears. This is also expected to reduce
OL,13,FUK reliance on imports of paper.
