OL,7,FHamdullah Eren, senior board member of
OL,8,Fthe Eren Holding group, said:
OL,9,F"Production at our new plant at
OL,10,FShotton Mill will be based on state-of-
OL,11,Fthe-art technology, making this the
OL,12,Fmost advanced paper campus in Europe.
OL,13,FOur custom-built plant will deliver
OL,14,Fsophisticated and sustainable
OL,15,Fmanufacturing solutions well into the
OL,16,F21st century.
