OL,7,F"This is the first major Eren Holding
OL,8,Fcap ex project outside Turkiye and we
OL,9,Fare delighted to have chosen Deeside
OL,10,Fas an ideal location to meet our
OL,11,Fambitions for growth. We are putting
OL,12,Fdown deep roots on a site of historic
OL,13,Findustrial significance.
OL,15,F"We believe this new plant will bring
OL,16,Fprosperity, leadership in our
OL,17,Findustry, and long-term employment
OL,18,Fprospects that will be the pride of
OL,19,FDeeside, Wales and Turkiye."
